main event: A saucer-shaped object was observed in Orting, Washington on August 6, 1965.
interesting points: The object was described as the size of a basketball, It emitted a humming sound and a broken crackle, The object was visible for 2-3 minutes before disappearing over a hill, Physical evidence of the sighting was noted, The conclusion of the report categorized the object as 'Ground Light'.
witness description: Mrs. Y, 31, a housewife from Orting, WA.
